C-1059 September Term 2017
081346 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2018

In the MATTER OF Request for Proposals #17DPP00144, Employee Benefits: Pharmacy Benefit Management Contract, OPTUMRX, INC., Petitioner

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004751-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
